rate-evening-of-tate-modern-lates-this-month-3784059">八月份，她还与泰特现代美术馆合作，策划了一场深夜的音乐、研讨会和对话活动</a>。</p><p> MTV EMA 由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rita-ora">Rita Ora</a>破纪录地第三次主持， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benson-boone">Benson Boone</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shawn-mendes">Shawn Mendes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">Teddy Swims</a> 、The warning、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peso-pluma">Peso Pluma</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyla">Tyla</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/busta-rhymes">Busta Rhymes</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pet-shop-boys">Pet Shop Boys</a>进行了现场表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-presents-busta-rhymes-with-the-global-icon-award-at-the-2024-mtv-emas-3811388">Little Simz 在 2024 年 MTV EMA 上向 Busta Rhymes 颁发全球偶像奖的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
